text: Falsamblesthis gracilis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Lameere in 1893. It is known from Venezuela.BioLib.cz - Falsamblesthis gracilis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Forsteriini Category:Beetles described in 1893
title: Falsamblesthis gracilis
